T02TD2376E:11a-1: bo dhi tsi tta bandha n'a ma /
T02TD2376E:11a-3: phyi nang byang chub sems bcing ba'i man ngag ces bya ba /
T02TD2376E:11a-4: byang chub sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2376E:11a-5: don dam kun rdzob byang chub sems //
T02TD2376E:11a-6: lhan cig skyes te mun pas bsgribs //
T02TD2376E:11a-7: kun du skye ba'i nyams len ni //
T02TD2376E:11a-8: bdag gis 'di ru bshad par bya //
T02TD2376E:11a-9: spyi bo'i gtsug nas bo la'i bar //
T02TD2376E:11a-10: sna tshogs rtsa ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD2376E:11a-11: de nas bde chen 'khor lo ru //
T02TD2376E:11a-12: sgo nga'i khog pa lta bu yi //
T02TD2376E:11a-13: byang chub sems la sems gtad nas //
T02TD2376E:11a-14: bo la'i rtse la rgyal lo tsam //
T02TD2376E:11a-15: gsal la sran rdog tsam du bsgom /
T02TD2376E:11a-16: bde chen sgo nga'i rtsa la ni //
T02TD2376E:11a-17: byang chub sems ni 'dzag par bya //
T02TD2376E:11a-18: lte ba'i bar du rnal 'byor kye //
T02TD2376E:11a-19: gnyis med bdud rtsis bkang byas nas //
T02TD2376E:11a-20: shes pa bde ba'i mchog tu 'gyur //
T02TD2376E:11a-21: sgom pa'i spyod yul phar mi spro //
T02TD2376E:11a-22: sems ni tshur la bkug mi bya //
T02TD2376E:11a-23: dper na sprul gyi mdud pa bzhin //
T02TD2376E:11a-24: sems ni rang grol gnas pa ste //
T02TD2376E:11a-25: dngos po'i bya ba bral 'gyur ba //
T02TD2376E:11a-26: rnal 'byor yid kyi zhen pa chod //
T02TD2376E:11a-27: mi n'a bdag gis rtogs pas grol //
T02TD2376E:11a-28: byang chub kyi sems bcing ba'i man ngag ces bya ba slob dpon mi n'a pas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
